{
  "texts": [
    "The recent state-of-the-art models, including GPT-4 [66], GPT-3 [65], Claude-3 [11], and Gemini 1.5 [69], exhibt strong capability in reasoning over text.",
    "Consequently, recent research increasingly employs LLMs alongside various language, vision, or multimodal models to enable advanced applications in various domains without the need for additional training [30,79,98].",
    "For example, IdealGPT combines two LLMs (GPT) with a visionand-language model to enable a framework that iteratively decomposes vision-and-language reasoning, where the two LLMs are treated as Questioner and Reasoner [99].",
    "Additionally, research has shown that LLMs possess the ability to reason with and interpret IoT sensor data [96].Recently, transformer-based Large language foundation models, such as GPT-4 [19], PaLM 2 [10], and LLaMA2 [90],have demonstrated superior performance across various medical-related NLP tasks.",
    "LLMs are used to enable various general healthcare applications."
  ]
}